 Bright room with balcony. It is available furnished with a bed, mattress, wardrobe, desk, and chair. The apartment has undergone complete renovation and was occupied in last April. It includes a modern kitchen with a dishwasher and a big bathroom. Washing machines and dryers are located in the basement, where there is also space for a bicycle. An elevator is also available. 

